# CookGPT - Cloud Kitchen Management System Walkthrough

## Overview
Built a comprehensive **Cloud Kitchen Management System API** using Django REST Framework with clean architecture and repository pattern. The API supports 3 user roles (Customer, Kitchen Admin, Delivery Agent) with 50 endpoints across 9 modules.

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["Presentation Layer<br/>(Views + Serializers)"] --> B["Application Layer<br/>(Services)"]
    B --> C["Domain Layer<br/>(Entities + DTOs + Interfaces)"]
    B --> D["Infrastructure Layer<br/>(Repositories + Models)"]
    D --> C
```

## Project Structure

| Layer | Path | Contents |
|---|---|---|
| **Domain** | `domain/` | 8 entities, 8 DTOs, 8 repository interfaces |
| **Application** | `application/` | 9 service interfaces, 9 service implementations |
| **Infrastructure** | `infrastructure/` | 13 Django ORM models, 8 concrete repositories |
| **Presentation** | `presentation/` | 30+ serializers, 50 API endpoints, role-based permissions |

## API Endpoints (50 total)

| Module | Endpoints | Key Operations |
|---|---|---|
| **Authentication** | 4 | Register, Login, Logout, Refresh Token |
| **Users** | 8 | Profile CRUD, Addresses, Change Password, List Users |
| **Menu** | 9 | Items CRUD, Categories, Image Upload, Search/Filter |
| **Orders** | 5 | Place Order, My Orders, All Orders, Update Status |
| **Cart** | 5 | Get Cart, Add/Remove/Update Items, Clear |
| **Payments** | 4 | Create, Get by ID/Order, Update Status |
| **Delivery** | 6 | Assign, Track, Update Status/Location, My Deliveries |
| **AI Bot** | 3 | Recipe Recommendations, History, Popular Ingredients |
| **Dashboard** | 6 | Stats, Sales Report, Popular Items, Kitchen Timers, Predictions |

## Key Features Implemented
- 🔐 **JWT Authentication** with HTTP-only cookie storage (24hr access / 7day refresh)
- 👥 **Role-based access control** (Customer, Kitchen Admin, Delivery Agent)
- 🤖 **AI Recipe Engine** with 12 built-in recipes, synonym matching, and scoring
- 📊 **Redis caching** for menu items, categories, and dashboard stats
- 🚚 **Real-time delivery tracking** with GPS coordinates
- ⏱️ **Kitchen Display System** (KDS) timers
- 📈 **Analytics dashboard** with sales reports and demand predictions

